name: Kickstart my Heart
description:
Collection #3 | Alessandra Aglietti

Similar to the work of Terry Gilliam, magical realism pervades the scene. Enthusiastic spectators witness a disturbing event, everything is normal, everything is wrong, everything is perfect...
At the bottom, the figures try in every way to keep the opera with its feet on the ground, but the fantasy has taken flight. It is too late.

Download the high resolution image on xdai.unique.one
